+Linux (System V style)
+~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+
+Start lightsd with:
+
+::
+
+   /etc/init.d/lightsd start
+
+Stop lightsd with:
+
+::
+
+   /etc/init.d/lightsd stop
+
+Check how lightsd is running with:
+
+::
+
+   ps aux | grep lightsd
+
+The logs will be logged to `syslogd(8)`_.
